  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p dir=\"ltr\">[Uncommon][Attack][Evocation][Dynamic Heightening]</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Traditions </strong>arcane, primal</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Access </strong>earth-bound</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Cast </strong>[two-actions] somatic, verbal</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Range </strong>30 feet</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With a sudden flick, you hurl jagged spikes of stone from your hoof. These spikes deal 3d4 points of piercing damage with a successful spell attack roll. On a critical hit, the target is stunned 1. If you are standing on stone when casting this spell, you may select a secondary target within range that takes half damage (compare both ACs against the same attack roll).</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Heightened (+1) The range is increased by 60 feet.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Heightened (+1) The damage is increased by 3d4.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Heightened (+1) The secondary target takes full damage.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Heightened (+2) The rocks become jagged and serrated, causing bleeding wounds. On a hit, the target suffers bleeding equal to the number of damage dice of the spell.</p>"
    },
